1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 4=

4
00:00:21,879 --> 00:00:22,879
Miss.

5
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:24,719
Miss Murong.

6
00:00:25,519 --> 00:00:27,000
I wouldn't let this beggar in.

7
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:28,320
Then he hit me...

8
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:31,120
(Murong Bingqing, Murong family)
He's right.

9
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:34,000
(Murong Bingqing, Murong family)
You've disgraced the Murong family.

10
00:00:34,759 --> 00:00:35,359
(Murong Bingqing, Murong family)
Get lost.

11
00:00:41,039 --> 00:00:43,159
You must be Murong Bingqing, right?

12
00:00:44,719 --> 00:00:45,799
Who are you?

13
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:47,640
I'm Peng Dasheng.

14
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:48,640
Years ago,

15
00:00:48,759 --> 00:00:50,000
your grandfather and my master

16
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:50,759
arranged a...

17
00:00:50,759 --> 00:00:52,119
My grandfather must have lost his mind.

18
00:00:52,439 --> 00:00:53,679
How could he choose someone like you

19
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:54,840
to marry into our family?

20
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:58,280
I'm not finished.

21
00:00:59,439 --> 00:01:00,439
No need.

22
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,679
My father already told me.

23
00:01:03,119 --> 00:01:05,239
That marriage agreement was
only my grandfather's passing joke.

24
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:09,239
With no clan or status to speak of,

25
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,879
you expect to be
part of the Murong family?

26
00:01:12,799 --> 00:01:13,959
Keep dreaming.

27
00:01:15,159 --> 00:01:16,799
How can you speak to someone like that?

28
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,200
And who is this?

29
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,760
Who I am doesn't matter.

30
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:30,040
Just know that I'm with Dasheng.

31
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:30,840
That's enough.

32
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:33,959
A man I never wanted,

33
00:01:34,319 --> 00:01:35,519
and you actually
treat him like a treasure?

34
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,280
Fine. I'll give him to you.

35
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:39,920
Hongxiu,

36
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,920
give them some silver notes.

37
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,239
Consider it compensation
for ending the engagement.

38
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,560
From now on,

39
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,239
don't let me see him again.

40
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,359
Miss Murong,

41
00:01:59,959 --> 00:02:01,200
I'll accept these silver notes

42
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,200
on behalf of my master.

43
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,040
I'll take this as your agreement

44
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,599
to end the engagement.

45
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,439
We won't disturb you anymore. Farewell.

46
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,039
Wait.

47
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:45,719
(Lin Dun, Heir of the Huxiao Manor)
Bingqing,

48
00:02:46,439 --> 00:02:47,439
(Lin Dun, Heir of the Huxiao Manor)
that guy over there must be

49
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:48,479
(Lin Dun, Heir of the Huxiao Manor)
the good-for-nothing

50
00:02:48,479 --> 00:02:50,800
(Lin Dun, Heir of the Huxiao Manor)
you were betrothed to, right?

51
00:02:56,159 --> 00:02:58,520
What an unpleasant mouth.

52
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:02,319
Who is this country girl?

53
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:04,840
Who are you calling unpleasant?

54
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,680
Whoever answers my question.

55
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,479
You dare insult me?

56
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:10,120
Someone!

57
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,520
Slap her. Teach her to watch her mouth.

58
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,479
Picking on a woman
isn't something to be proud of.

59
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:17,919
Big guy,

60
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:18,960
if you want a fight,

61
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,840
I'll take you on.

62
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:24,719
A country bumpkin like you

63
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,080
thinks you're worthy of fighting me?

64
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,080
You're not worthy.

65
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:30,479
Exactly. Mr. Lin

66
00:03:30,479 --> 00:03:31,639
is the heir of Huxiao Manor,

67
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:33,120
the greatest escort agency in Jiangnan.

68
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:34,639
In Gusu,

69
00:03:34,759 --> 00:03:36,159
he's someone no one dares cross.

70
00:03:36,879 --> 00:03:39,120
I thought you were some noble family.

71
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,719
Turns out
you're just a bunch of bullies.

72
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,080
Say that again.

73
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:45,639
Mr. Lin,
my father is hosting guests today.

74
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:46,960
Please don't cause trouble.

75
00:03:51,639 --> 00:03:53,479
Listen carefully, brat.

76
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:56,199
Tomorrow is Bingqing's

77
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:57,599
martial arts marriage contest.

78
00:03:57,680 --> 00:04:00,759
When that day comes,
someone as insignificant as you

79
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:03,000
better stay far away.

80
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:04,840
Don't ruin the occasion.

81
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,840
I don't understand.

82
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:09,800
My legs belong to me.

83
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:12,280
Whether I leave or stay
is none of your business.

84
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:17,560
I get it now.

85
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,240
You think

86
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,959
I'm going to join tomorrow's contest

87
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,040
and steal your glory, don't you?

88
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,920
Brat,

89
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:29,120
you're deliberately provoking me.

90
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:31,160
Why do you treat everyone like a target?

91
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,000
What do you mean?

92
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:35,959
Because you're the kind of arrow
that's always looking for a target.

93
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,160
You have a death wish!

94
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,639
Brat,

95
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,600
your qi sea is empty.

96
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,240
You don't have a trace of inner force.

97
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:53,040
And you still dare challenge me?

98
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:54,959
Someone like you

99
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:57,000
isn't worth me using my inner force.

100
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,879
You don't know your place.

101
00:04:58,879 --> 00:04:59,680
Enough.

102
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,199
Peng Dasheng,

103
00:05:03,839 --> 00:05:05,079
if you keep causing trouble,

104
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,160
don't blame me for throwing you
out of Gusu.

105
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:09,839
Did you hear that?
Someone like you doesn't belong here.

106
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:11,199
Leave now!

107
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:12,040
Fine.

108
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,600
Very well.

109
00:05:14,399 --> 00:05:15,319
Murong Bingqing,

110
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,680
I was planning
to leave Gusu today anyway.

111
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:21,000
But now, I've changed my mind.

112
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:25,000
I'll definitely attend

113
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,399
your martial arts marriage contest
tomorrow.

114
00:05:26,839 --> 00:05:29,040
And I'll defeat everyone there.

115
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,639
Then, I'll make you say

116
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,199
in front of everyone,

117
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:33,399
"Dear,

118
00:05:34,199 --> 00:05:35,000
I was wrong."

119
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,600
Brat,

120
00:05:40,879 --> 00:05:42,680
are you still dreaming?

121
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,000
With your empty qi sea

122
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,839
and no inner force,

123
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:49,519
you probably couldn't even beat our dog.

124
00:05:50,199 --> 00:05:51,279
If I were you,

125
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:53,399
I'd find somewhere to hide.

126
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:55,319
Anything is better than
embarrassing yourself.

127
00:05:58,439 --> 00:06:00,959
Brat, listen carefully.

128
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:04,399
I'll give you one day to leave Gusu.

129
00:06:04,839 --> 00:06:05,720
Otherwise,

130
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:10,279
I'll make sure
you never see another sunrise.

131
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,800
Then remember this!

132
00:06:15,399 --> 00:06:17,240
The humiliation I suffered today,

133
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:21,160
I'll definitely repay it one day.

134
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:22,879
Xiaojiu,

135
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:24,199
let's go.

136
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,079
You...

137
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:30,399
Bingqing.

138
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,279
It's only been a few days,

139
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,959
but you look thinner.

140
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,600
Mr. Lin,

141
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,160
I have something to handle.

142
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,759
Please excuse me.

143
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:42,240
Wait, Bingqing...

144
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:47,879
Mr. Lin, are we heading home?

145
00:06:49,439 --> 00:06:50,720
Ignorant fool!

146
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:52,399
Please forgive me, Mr. Lin.

147
00:06:54,839 --> 00:06:56,199
Murong Bingqing...

148
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:59,959
One day, I'll make you kneel before me

149
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:01,560
and beg for my love.

150
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:06,959
Miss, you've always been kind to others.

151
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:10,519
Why were you so harsh to Peng Dasheng?

152
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:16,519
People often become trapped
by things they can't have.

153
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,720
Letting him give up completely

154
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:20,959
is better than
letting him hold onto hope

155
00:07:21,439 --> 00:07:22,560
and suffer more.

156
00:07:22,759 --> 00:07:23,920
But by doing this, Miss,

157
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,839
aren't you making yourself look cruel?

158
00:07:27,079 --> 00:07:29,720
If it helps Peng Dasheng suffer less,

159
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:32,199
then perhaps it's worth it.

160
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,959
(Murong Xiang)
Seeing you understand things so well

161
00:07:38,399 --> 00:07:39,800
(Head of the Murong family)
truly makes me proud.

162
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:43,519
Father, weren't you hosting guests
in the front hall?

163
00:07:43,879 --> 00:07:45,480
I heard you met him.

164
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:54,000
Back then, the Murong family
had fallen on hard times

165
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:55,639
and was looked down upon by other clans.

166
00:07:56,279 --> 00:07:58,759
Your grandfather was almost killed
by those villains.

167
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:02,439
Luckily,
a wandering Daoist saved his life.

168
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:03,959
That was how he survived.

169
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:07,040
To repay that kindness,

170
00:08:07,319 --> 00:08:08,759
your grandfather accepted this marriage

171
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:10,439
without telling me.

172
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:12,879
But now,

173
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:15,399
the Murong family
stands at the top of the martial world.

174
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:18,800
Your marriage
cannot be decided so casually anymore.

175
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,720
Don't worry.

176
00:08:21,319 --> 00:08:22,079
I will find you

177
00:08:22,079 --> 00:08:24,319
a husband who truly suits you.

178
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:29,199
Thank you for worrying about
my marriage, Father.

179
00:08:31,959 --> 00:08:35,639
Dasheng, you said you were going to join
the martial arts marriage contest.

180
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:36,919
Were you serious?

181
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:40,000
Back then, my master
saved the Murong family's head.

182
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,799
The Murong family owed him a great debt.

183
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,600
But instead of repaying his kindness,
they turned against us

184
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,320
and treated our engagement like a joke.

185
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:47,320
There's a saying:

186
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:48,200
"If you want to keep your dignity,

187
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,320
you have to fight for it."

188
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,440
Today, I'll stand up for my master

189
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,799
and repay this humiliation.

190
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:53,759
That's right.

191
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:55,000
By the way,

192
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:58,639
that annoying guy said
your qi sea was empty.

193
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:01,159
But you defeated the Northern Evil Duo.

194
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,639
How could you have no inner force?

195
00:09:03,799 --> 00:09:05,159
Actually, he was right.

196
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,559
My qi sea

197
00:09:06,559 --> 00:09:07,759
really is empty.

198
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:09,080
Hurry.

199
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,039
Hurry.

200
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,039
Careful.

201
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,120
Dasheng,

202
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,200
let's go see what's going on.

203
00:09:15,039 --> 00:09:16,159
Slow down. Watch your step.

204
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:18,440
(Xuanmiao Temple)
Infinite blessings.

205
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:20,840
(Xuanmiao Temple)
With all the young men gathered here,

206
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,840
our temple is truly honored.

207
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,799
As everyone knows, our late master

208
00:09:24,799 --> 00:09:27,559
- left a final instruction.
- Hurry up!

209
00:09:27,559 --> 00:09:30,919
Today shall be the day the Tianji Armor
finds its destined master.

210
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:33,799
As the saying goes,
a treasured sword belongs to a hero.

211
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:36,639
We hope all of you will show your skills

212
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:40,480
so that we can find the rightful owner
of this legendary armor.

213
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:46,480
What exactly is the Tianji Armor?

214
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:50,360
You don't even know what it is?

215
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:53,080
What a country bumpkin.

216
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:54,480
This armor was forged

217
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:57,080
from Froststeel Essence,
a material as hard as diamond.

218
00:09:57,360 --> 00:10:00,320
The master smith also added
Heavenly Meteor Iron

219
00:10:00,639 --> 00:10:03,399
and spent three full years
crafting it with care.

220
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,320
That's how the unrivaled

221
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:07,000
Tianji Armor was made.

222
00:10:10,919 --> 00:10:12,159
After all that hype,

223
00:10:12,159 --> 00:10:13,519
it's still just armor.

224
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:14,679
They're making it sound
far more mysterious than it is.

225
00:10:14,679 --> 00:10:15,320
What?

226
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:18,759
What would someone like you know?

227
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:23,360
This armor is a rare Mystic Rank
protective armor in the martial world.

228
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,559
Wearing it is like gaining

229
00:10:24,559 --> 00:10:27,360
half an indestructible body.

230
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:31,159
Countless martial artists
have fought for it,

231
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:32,600
yet no one has ever obtained it.

232
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,080
A treasure this precious

233
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:36,039
is beyond your understanding.

234
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:40,200
Any young man
who wishes to claim this armor

235
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,679
may step forward.

236
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:44,200
Channel your genuine qi

237
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,559
and merge it with the armor.

238
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:48,039
If the armor accepts you,
it will recognize you as its master.

239
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:51,679
If it doesn't,
then you are simply not destined for it.

240
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:52,919
Everyone,

241
00:10:52,919 --> 00:10:55,000
you may begin your attempts.

242
00:10:59,799 --> 00:11:00,919
Dasheng,

243
00:11:01,399 --> 00:11:03,120
if this armor is so powerful and rare,

244
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,879
why is no one trying?

245
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:05,720
I don't know.

246
00:11:05,919 --> 00:11:06,480
Miss.

247
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:12,279
Miss, this armor is extremely selective.

248
00:11:12,399 --> 00:11:14,960
Only someone with great fortune
can control it.

249
00:11:15,639 --> 00:11:17,120
If someone forces themselves to wear it,

250
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:19,840
they'll be overwhelmed by its power.

251
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:22,240
At best, they'll suffer unbearable pain.

252
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:25,120
At worst,
their meridians will be destroyed.

253
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,639
Everyone,

254
00:11:27,759 --> 00:11:29,759
is anyone willing to try?

255
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:30,879
I'll try.

256
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,120
Good.

257
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,120
Could he be

258
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,639
the legendary first disciple

259
00:11:43,639 --> 00:11:45,440
of the Kunlun Sect,

260
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:47,519
Kun Zhongyu?

261
00:11:47,919 --> 00:11:48,600
That's right.

262
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:51,200
I am Kun Zhongyu,

263
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,080
(Kun Zhongyu)
known throughout the northeast region,

264
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:55,679
(First disciple of Kunlun Sect)
as the Flying Dragon Swordsman.

265
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,919
I don't see a flying dragon.

266
00:11:59,919 --> 00:12:01,480
But all I see is a flying pig.

267
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:06,360
Sir, before you try the armor,

268
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:08,159
I must remind you of one thing.

269
00:12:08,399 --> 00:12:11,159
If your inner energy becomes blocked

270
00:12:11,159 --> 00:12:12,720
and you cannot activate the armor,

271
00:12:12,759 --> 00:12:15,080
stop using your inner force immediately.

272
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:18,919
Do not force yourself just to save face.

273
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:22,080
Otherwise, you'll be struck back
by the armor's spiritual power.

274
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:24,039
Okay, understood.

275
00:12:24,039 --> 00:12:25,559
Then I'll begin, sir.

276
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:44,720
As expected of
Kunlun Sect's first disciple.

277
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,440
Such powerful, genuine qi

278
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,639
is rarely seen.

279
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,559
I'd say

280
00:12:48,559 --> 00:12:51,440
Mr. Kun's cultivation has
already reached above the fifth rank.

281
00:12:51,519 --> 00:12:53,000
Among the martial artists
in the martial world,

282
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:55,080
he is truly exceptional.

283
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:59,360
Dasheng, do you think he can succeed?

284
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:03,200
Him? He's forcing the armor
with his genuine qi.

285
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,759
He won't last much longer
before running out of strength.

286
00:13:04,919 --> 00:13:07,559
He's only suffering because
he cares too much about his pride.

287
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,559
Look.

288
00:13:21,879 --> 00:13:24,639
What a pity.
But the armor chooses its master

289
00:13:24,799 --> 00:13:25,879
by fate.

290
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:28,320
You shouldn't force it.

291
00:13:30,879 --> 00:13:31,440
Fine.

292
00:13:31,639 --> 00:13:34,600
I underestimated
the armor's spiritual power.

293
00:13:34,639 --> 00:13:36,159
I failed because

294
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:38,360
I didn't give it my all.

295
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:41,840
He's not strong enough,

296
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:43,639
yet he sure talks big.

297
00:13:43,879 --> 00:13:44,679
Who?

298
00:13:47,799 --> 00:13:49,080
Who said that?

299
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,000
Who was it?

300
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:54,480
(Xuanmiao Temple)

301
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:59,120
(Xuanmiao Temple)

302
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:11,919
May I ask

303
00:14:11,919 --> 00:14:13,000
your name and master?

304
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:15,639
I'm Peng Dasheng.

305
00:14:15,679 --> 00:14:17,120
I trained under the Wuhuduandao Sect.

306
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:19,039
Da... Dasheng?

307
00:14:19,399 --> 00:14:20,960
Wuhuduandao Sect?

308
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:21,759
Never heard of it.

309
00:14:22,159 --> 00:14:24,200
Are you rushing off to forge iron,

310
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:26,360
or are you rushing off
to the West to fetch scriptures?

311
00:14:31,399 --> 00:14:32,840
Then let me ask you this.

312
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:34,759
You used all your strength
to pull back your energy just now,

313
00:14:34,759 --> 00:14:36,399
but the armor didn't move at all.

314
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:38,000
And you still say you underestimated it?

315
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:40,159
Looks like you already used
everything you had.

316
00:14:40,159 --> 00:14:41,120
Hey,

317
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:41,960
what nonsense are you saying?

318
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,279
I'm talking about you.

319
00:14:43,639 --> 00:14:45,759
My master
was kind enough to spare your pride.

320
00:14:45,759 --> 00:14:47,120
He didn't say out loud
that you had failed.

321
00:14:47,559 --> 00:14:49,240
Yet you still won't let it go.

322
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:51,200
Someone as narrow-minded as you

323
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:52,759
is truly rare.

324
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:11,200
I suppose the person who just arrived
must be the famous

325
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:13,360
Mr. Charming,

326
00:15:13,799 --> 00:15:14,600
Xiao Ziting.

327
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:15,919
As expected of the young master

328
00:15:15,919 --> 00:15:18,159
of Nongxiao Pavilion in Jiangbei.

329
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:22,559
(Xiao Ziting, Nongxiao Pavilion)
He's truly elegant and extraordinary.

330
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:26,720
Mr. Xiao! Mr. Xiao! Mr. Xiao!

331
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:27,840
He's here! He's here!

332
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:29,919
(Mr. Xiao)
Mr. Xiao! Mr. Xiao!

333
00:15:29,919 --> 00:15:31,519
(Azure Fan Young Master, Eternal Hero)
Mr. Xiao! Mr. Xiao!

334
00:15:31,679 --> 00:15:33,279
(Azure Fan Young Master, Eternal Hero)
A dazzling glory!

335
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,960
Today, he makes his debut!

336
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,519
His name will be known
across the martial world!

337
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:38,440
Mr. Xiao!

338
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,120
Mr. Xiao!

339
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:52,960
Cuizhu. Cuizhu, come here.

340
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:55,120
Where did you find

341
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:56,399
so many oddballs?

342
00:15:56,519 --> 00:15:58,720
Mr. Xiao, we're unfamiliar with Gusu.

343
00:15:58,840 --> 00:16:00,720
It took me a lot of effort
to gather these people.

344
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:02,639
Young man, let me ask you something.

345
00:16:02,799 --> 00:16:04,480
Didn't you say that after we sign,

346
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:05,799
we'd get some flatbread?

347
00:16:05,799 --> 00:16:08,480
Yeah.

348
00:16:08,919 --> 00:16:10,200
Are you insane? What bread?

349
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,480
Take her to get the bread
that never exists!

350
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:13,679
Where's the bread?

351
00:16:13,679 --> 00:16:14,960
We want ours too.

352
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:17,279
I'm not leaving without it.

353
00:16:17,279 --> 00:16:18,080
Well...

354
00:16:18,559 --> 00:16:20,039
I was carried away
by my reputation just now.

355
00:16:20,039 --> 00:16:21,480
Please forgive my foolish display.

356
00:16:21,639 --> 00:16:22,240
My apologies.

357
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:23,519
Mr. Xiao,

358
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:24,879
you came at just the right time.

359
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:27,559
This man insulted me today.

360
00:16:27,559 --> 00:16:29,080
I wish to settle this
with him in a duel.

361
00:16:29,159 --> 00:16:30,720
You can witness it for us.

362
00:16:32,039 --> 00:16:33,879
It was only a joke.

363
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:35,960
Why take it so seriously, Zhongyu?

364
00:16:36,279 --> 00:16:39,600
Xiao Ziting, you didn't come here
just to mock me, did you?

365
00:16:39,759 --> 00:16:40,759
That's not true.

366
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:42,360
To be honest,

367
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:44,840
I'm here to see if the armor
will choose me as its master.

368
00:16:52,940 --> 00:16:53,420
♪Come on♪

369
00:16:56,940 --> 00:16:58,620
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

370
00:17:00,580 --> 00:17:03,540
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

371
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:06,740
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

372
00:17:06,980 --> 00:17:09,820
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

373
00:17:10,220 --> 00:17:12,820
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

374
00:17:13,340 --> 00:17:16,300
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

375
00:17:16,540 --> 00:17:19,540
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

376
00:17:19,700 --> 00:17:22,620
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

377
00:17:22,780 --> 00:17:25,540
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

378
00:17:26,100 --> 00:17:29,420
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

379
00:17:29,460 --> 00:17:32,460
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

380
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:38,140
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

381
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:40,580
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

382
00:17:41,140 --> 00:17:43,660
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

383
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:46,780
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

384
00:17:46,900 --> 00:17:50,580
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

385
00:17:51,180 --> 00:17:53,300
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

386
00:17:54,220 --> 00:17:56,340
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

387
00:17:56,500 --> 00:17:59,780
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

388
00:17:59,820 --> 00:18:04,100
♪I am my own king♪

389
00:18:17,180 --> 00:18:18,740
♪I emerge into the world♪

390
00:18:18,740 --> 00:18:20,500
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

391
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:21,860
♪My pride is my trump card♪

392
00:18:21,860 --> 00:18:23,660
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

393
00:18:23,660 --> 00:18:25,060
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

394
00:18:25,060 --> 00:18:26,820
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

395
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:28,340
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

396
00:18:28,340 --> 00:18:30,060
♪I dare to break every rule♪

397
00:18:30,060 --> 00:18:31,380
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

398
00:18:31,380 --> 00:18:33,220
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

399
00:18:33,220 --> 00:18:34,460
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

400
00:18:34,460 --> 00:18:36,700
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

401
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:38,220
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

402
00:18:38,220 --> 00:18:39,820
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

403
00:18:39,820 --> 00:18:41,420
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

404
00:18:41,420 --> 00:18:43,140
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

405
00:18:43,140 --> 00:18:44,860
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

406
00:18:44,860 --> 00:18:46,220
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

407
00:18:46,220 --> 00:18:47,860
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

408
00:18:47,860 --> 00:18:49,340
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

409
00:18:49,340 --> 00:18:51,060
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

410
00:18:51,060 --> 00:18:52,660
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

411
00:18:52,660 --> 00:18:54,220
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

412
00:18:54,220 --> 00:18:58,540
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

413
00:18:58,540 --> 00:19:00,700
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

414
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:03,300
♪Let me write the legend♪

415
00:19:08,180 --> 00:19:10,740
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

416
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:14,060
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

417
00:19:14,060 --> 00:19:16,540
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

418
00:19:16,540 --> 00:19:20,620
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

419
00:19:20,980 --> 00:19:23,580
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

420
00:19:23,700 --> 00:19:26,060
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

421
00:19:26,060 --> 00:19:29,100
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

422
00:19:29,100 --> 00:19:34,140
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
